<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Sign Up</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.1.min.js"
        integrity="sha256-o88AwQnZB+VDvE9tvIXrMQaPlFFSUTR+nldQm1LuPXQ=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/register.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/homepage.css" type="text/css">

</head>

<body>
    <form action="/register" method="post">
        <div class="header">
            <p>♡ שליח עד הבית חינם בקנייה של 249 ש"ח ♡</p>

            <div id="optionsbar">
                <ul id="optionsmenu1">
                    <li><button class="btn btn-light">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor"
                                class="bi bi-bag-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path
                                    d="M8 1a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.5 2.5V4h-5v-.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 8 1zm3.5 3v-.5a3.5 3.5 0 1 0-7 0V4H1v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4h-3.5z" />
                            </svg></button>
                    </li>
                    <li><button class="btn btn-light"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16"
                                fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-heart-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                                    d="M8 1.314C12.438-3.248 23.534 4.735 8 15-7.534 4.736 3.562-3.248 8 1.314z" />
                            </svg> </button></li>

                    <li>
                        <div class="logo"><a href="/"><img src="../public/logo.png"
                                    style="height: 2.2cm; width: 2cm;margin-left: 17cm; margin-right: 19cm;"></a></div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="signup-form">
                <form action="/register" method="post">
                    <h1>טופס הרשמה</h1>
                    <p>בבקשה תמלא/י את המידע הבא כדי ליצור משתמש באתר</p>

                    <input type="username" name="username" placeholder="שם משתמש">
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="סיסמה">
                    <input type="address" name="address" placeholder="כתובת">
                    <input type="phonenumber" name="phonenumber" placeholder="טלפון">
                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-light" style="border: 2px solid black;margin-top:10px"
                        value="להרשמה">
                </form>
            </div>

            יש לך כבר משתמש באתר? <a href="/login">התחבר/י</a>
</body>

</html>